OK, I'm not sure where it's supposed to come from. Maybe it's from the assets and bazel failed to fetch them.

Can you look at tensorflow/examples/android/assets? Is it there?

If you download the inception file:

$ curl -L https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/inception5h.zip -o /tmp/inception5h.zip
$ unzip -v /tmp/inception5h.zip

Is it there?

body:
OK, I'm not sure where it's supposed to come from. Maybe it's from the assets and bazel failed to fetch them.

Can you look at `tensorflow/examples/android/assets`? Is it there?

If you download the inception file:

```
$ curl -L https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/inception5h.zip -o /tmp/inception5h.zip
$ unzip -v /tmp/inception5h.zip
```

Is it there?
